<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/27203367">如何看待把妹知识？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3064229" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">百度百科：泡学是包括了很多方面技术与艺术的<a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/2276055.htm" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">综合学科<i class="icon-external"></i></a>，如：<a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/84616.htm" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">搭讪<i class="icon-external"></i></a>、吸引、约会、<a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/254407.htm" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">诱惑<i class="icon-external"></i></a>、恋爱、<a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/8496.htm" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">婚姻<i class="icon-external"></i></a>、社交等等。其中每个专门的学问都可以独立成一个子学科，例如搭讪学、约会学、恋爱学、吸引学等等。</div>


</div>
